extends layout.pug

//- This pug file dynamically renders the landing page. On the landing page, information is pulled from data.json
//- and rendered to create the dynamic gallery of projects and project links. This pug file also controls the 
//- content on the left hand side of the screen. (Note to self: Images in this section are 550px x 550px).

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div
      h1 Welcome to My Portfolio!
      p.lead.text-light
        | I am a Masters in Computer and Information Technology student at the University of Pennsylvania. This is a portfolio to showcase my work as a developer. I have implemented a wide range of technologies in my projects including Java, C, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, node.js, Express, and more! Check out some of my projects in the gallery below or click "Learn More" to learn more about me!
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3
      each project in projects 
        .cell
          a(href=`/project/${project.id}`)
            img.thumbnail(src=`${project.image_urls[0]}`)
            h5= project.project_name
